    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Up for sale is a driver-focused 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This unit delivers linear power through six individual throttle bodies and is mated to a crisp 6-speed Getrag manual transmission. Mechanical integrity is paramount; the VANOS system has been recently serviced, and the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced to ensure chassis rigidity during high-lateral-G cornering. It retains a factory limited-slip differential for optimal traction and a balanced suspension geometry that provides exceptional communicative feedback through the rack-and-pinion steering. While showing honest signs of use consistent with its mileage, this example remains a visceral, high-revving masterpiece of M-division engineering.",
