      "description": "This 2018 Executive Sport SUV is a testament to careful ownership and consistent maintenance. The exterior is finished in a deep metallic charcoal that retains a brilliant shine, showing only minor, inevitable stone chips on the lower front valance from standard highway driving. Inside, the cabin remains a sanctuary of comfort; the genuine leather seats are supple and free of cracks or stains, and the dual-zone climate control and heated steering wheel function perfectly. Every electronic feature, from the premium surround-sound system to the intuitive navigation display, is in full working order. Mechanically, the car is robust and reliable, having undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection just last month. The engine delivers smooth, responsive power, and the transmission shifts seamlessly through all gears. With a complete service history and tires that retain significant tread depth, this vehicle offers a sophisticated driving experience without the 'new car' price tag.",
